          "id": "e81a02e95a6d4dd47b7f39f38877ed9e7663db6a",
          "message": "feat(benchmark): add Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-MXFP4 to nightly benchmark (#536)\n\nAdd amd/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-MXFP4-Preview as a dense model benchmark\ntarget. Runs on TP1 (single MI355X, ~35GB MXFP4 fits in 288GB VRAM).\nProvides a dense model baseline alongside existing MoE models.\n\nValidated per .claude/commands/add-model.md:\n- llama.py model + LlamaForCausalLM registration already exist\n- Accuracy test entry already in models_accuracy.json (threshold 0.88)\n- Smoke tested model loading on mi355-gpu-15\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
